{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"stepbystep","title":"stepbystep","subLink":null},{"id":"1)registerthemodule","title":"1) Register The Module","subLink":[]},{"id":"2)copytheuicomponents","title":"2) Copy the Ui components","subLink":[]},{"id":"3)designthejson","title":"3) Design the Json","subLink":[]},{"id":"4)createtheform","title":"4) Create the Form","subLink":[]},{"id":"5)htmlimplementation","title":"5) Html Implementation","subLink":[]},{"id":"result","title":"Result","subLink":[]}],"title":"Step By Step Design","description":"","validatorType":"template-driven","validationTypeTitle":"Template Driven Decorator","type":"simple","category":"dynamic-forms","subCategory":null,"linkTitle":"stepbystep","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class='row page-section' id= '1)registerthemodule'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>1) Register The Module<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#1)registerthemodule'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >First You need to import the <span class='highlighted'>RxDynamicReactiveFormsModule</span> in the app module.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-module-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= '2)copytheuicomponents'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>2) Copy the Ui components<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#2)copytheuicomponents'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >You need to copy the bootstrap component file for using the controls and ui features from here <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/dynamic-forms/dynamicbootstrap/validators\"><span class='highlighted'>Boostrap.component.ts</span></a></p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= '3)designthejson'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>3) Design the Json<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#3)designthejson'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The second step is to define the json data which comes from the server. The Json data is stored in the form of <span class='highlighted'>serverData</span>.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-serverData-component\"></div>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To Bind the formControl to the user interface, you have to define in the <span class='highlighted'>uiBindings</span>.</p>\r\n<blockquote class='showHideElement' ><p>Note : If you want to change the order of the formControls in the user Interface. You must do it in <span class='highlighted'>uiBindings</span></p></blockquote>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-ui-component\"></div>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Based on which layout you want define the <span class='highlighted'>viewMode</span> that can be either bootstrap-basic,bootstrap-horizontal or bootstrap-advance</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-viewmode-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= '4)createtheform'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>4) Create the Form<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#4)createtheform'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The Third Step is to create a form using <span class='highlighted'>dynamicForm</span> method of <span class='highlighted'>RxFormBuilder</span>. In that you pass the serverData and dynamicFormConfiguration as below.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-form-component\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= '5)htmlimplementation'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>5) Html Implementation<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#5)htmlimplementation'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The Fourth and last step is to pass the html tag in the template using <span class='highlighted'>rxweb-dynamic-form</span> and pass the dynamicFormBuildConfig as <span class='highlighted'>rxDynamicForm</span> in the form tag</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"step-by-step-form-html\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'result'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Result<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/dynamic-forms/stepbystep/template-driven/decorators#result'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-complete\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}